    <section id="block-block-9" class="block block-block column1 clearfix">

        <h2 class="block-title">Bower Cottage</h2>
    
  <p><a href="/bower-cottage"><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/all/themes/bowercottage/images/col1.jpg" /></a></p>
<h2>Bower Cottage</h2>
<p>Bower Cottage Accommodation in Blackheath is an elegant, warm and inviting cottage or an elevated studio apartment, secluded on over an acre, bordering the World Heritage listed Blue Mountains National Park. </p>
<div class="button"><a href="/bower-cottage">read more</a></div>

</section>
  </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
            <div class="region region-front-col2">
    <section id="block-block-10" class="block block-block column2 clearfix">

        <h2 class="block-title">A Bower Above</h2>
    
  <p><a href="/a-bower-above"><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/all/themes/bowercottage/images/col2.jpg" /></a></p>
<h2>A Bower Above</h2>
<p>A Bower Above is a sunlit, north facing, studio apartment. Architecturally designed with passive solar principles in mind, you'll enjoy sunrise to sunset warmth, with a gas log, slow combustion style fire to keep you beautifully warm in the cool of the evenings.</p>
<div class="button"><a href="/a-bower-above">read more</a></div>

</section>
  </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
            <div class="region region-front-col3">
    <section id="block-block-11" class="block block-block column3 clearfix">

        <h2 class="block-title">Map and Directions</h2>
    
  <p><a href="/contacts-and-map"><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/all/themes/bowercottage/images/col3map.jpg" /></a></p>
<h2>Map &amp; Directions</h2>
<p>Bower Cottage Accommodation is situated on the outskirts of the beautiful mountain top township of Blackheath, one and a half to two hours drive west of Sydney's CBD.</p>
<div class="button"><a href="/contacts-and-map">read more</a></div>

</section>
